Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 70th Weekly Dose of Optimism.
We=E2=80=99re sending everyone a happy belated Thanksgiving, and we hope yo=
u were able to spend it with family, friends, and loved ones. There=E2=80=
=99s a lot to be thankful for over here at Not Boring HQ, and none of it wo=
uld be possible without you. Thank you for reading, sharing, and spending y=
our time with us.
We=E2=80=99re keeping it sweet and simple this week, just links and quotes,=
 to maximize family time=E2=80=A6and also because it=E2=80=99s Black Friday=
, a very busy day for Dan! His company, Create [ https://substack.com/redir=
ect/463b5b2a-b20d-4c0e-ae57-776b8b6b0fda?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_=
ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], is running their best offer of the year=
: 30% off all orders + free Create trucker hat (when you spend $100).  If y=
ou=E2=80=99re looking to kick-off your post-Thanksgiving fitness routine or=
 load up on the perfect tasty-but-healthy stocking stuffer, check out Creat=
e=E2=80=99s new Blue Raspberry creatine gummies [ https://substack.com/redi=
rect/463b5b2a-b20d-4c0e-ae57-776b8b6b0fda?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA=
_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]=E2=80=A6they are delish.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
(1) Israel=E2=80=93Hamas war: The hostage deal and ceasefire explained [ ht=
tps://substack.com/redirect/0aea4557-9797-46d8-9972-aaa391b9fde4?j=3DeyJ1Ij=
oiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
From Reuters
Israel and Palestinian Islamist group Hamas will start a four-day truce on =
Friday morning with the first batch of Israeli hostages released later that=
 day, mediators in Qatar said.
Under the Israel-Hamas deal, the two sides agreed to a four-day truce so th=
at 50 women and children under the age of 19 taken hostage could be freed i=
n return for 150 Palestinian women and teenagers in Israeli detention.
(2) OpenAI Made an AI Breakthrough Before Altman Firing, Stoking Excitement=
 and Concern [ https://substack.com/redirect/33407700-0988-4efd-bb7c-706212=
cf3496?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
Jon Victor [ https://substack.com/redirect/a6ba25bf-716c-4970-9fdd-2696a71b=
41c1?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] A=
mir Efrati [ https://substack.com/redirect/68833da4-a598-4315-a4fa-df0f5f05=
34f2?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] f=
or the Information
In the following months, senior OpenAI researchers used the innovation to b=
uild systems that could solve basic math problems, a difficult task for exi=
sting AI models. Jakub Pachocki and Szymon Sidor, two top researchers, used=
 Sutskever=E2=80=99s work to build a model called Q* (pronounced =E2=80=9CQ=
-Star=E2=80=9D) that was able to solve math problems that it hadn=E2=80=99t=
 seen before, an important technical milestone. A demo of the model circula=
ted within OpenAI in recent weeks, and the pace of development alarmed some=
 researchers focused on AI safety.
(3) Large-scale pancreatic cancer detection via non-contrast CT and deep le=
arning [ https://substack.com/redirect/7e7cab41-c12e-4ce7-8cc3-852abeba7844=
?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
From Nature
Here, we develop a deep learning approach, pancreatic cancer detection with=
 artificial intelligence (PANDA), that can detect and classify pancreatic l=
esions with high accuracy via non-contrast CT. PANDA is trained on a datase=
t of 3,208 patients from a single center. PANDA achieves an area under the =
receiver operating characteristic curve (AUC) of 0.986=E2=80=930.996 for le=
sion detection in a multicenter validation involving 6,239 patients across =
10 centers, outperforms the mean radiologist performance by 34.1% in sensit=
ivity and 6.3% in specificity for PDAC identification, and achieves a sensi=
tivity of 92.9% and specificity of 99.9% for lesion detection in a real-wor=
ld multi-scenario validation consisting of 20,530 consecutive patients.
(4) FDA adopts Operation Warp Speed lessons for rare disease pilot program =
[ https://substack.com/redirect/52610133-887c-490f-aad6-5acf9aecf61f?j=3Dey=
